here is a list of psychologist bf skinners books 
the behavior of organisms 1938 
walden two 1948 
science and human behavior 1953 
verbal behavior 1957 
schedules of reinforcement with charles b ferster 1957 
cumulative record 1959 revised 1961 1972 
the analysis of behavior with james g holland 1961 
the technology of teaching 1968 
contingencies of reinforcement a theoretical analysis 1969 
beyond freedom and dignity 1971 
about behavorism 1974 
particulars of my life 1976 
reflections on behavorism and society 1978 
the shaping of a behavorist 1979 
notebooks 1980 
a matter of consequences 1983 
enjoy old age 1983 
upon further reflection 1986 
