supreme court summoned the woman now 30 to the witness stand by 
now everyone knew who she was there was silence for 2 minutes as 
spectators and reporters waited tension building for the arrival 
of the central park jogger 
she took her seat slowly assisted by a court officer a jagged 
scar ran along her face mute testimony to the viciousness of her 
attackers in a steady voice she detailed the lasting effects of 
the beating she cant remember 
i have problems with balance when im walking and 
