her testimony her method of birth control the last time she made 
love with her boyfriend a defense lawyer in his closing argument 
suggested she stopped for a tryst on her way to the park and had 
never been raped 
much of her background is well known a pennsylvania native 
holder of graduate degrees from yale a wall street investment 
banker a hard worker a dedicated runner family members say she 
holds no grudges and remains determined in her recovery 
but no one can say what the future holds for the central park 
jogger other than to say it cant be like the past 
the fact that she could even come to this courtroom is a 
miracle assistant district attorney elizabeth lederer told the 
jury in her closing argument the jogger will never be the same 
as she was 
